org.mmbase.util

Class LRUHashtable<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mmbase.util.LRUHashtable<K,V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, Map<K,V>, CacheImplementationInterface<K,V>, SizeMeasurable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MultilevelCacheHandler
    Deprecated. 
    use org.mmbase.cache.implementation.LRUCache

    public class LRUHashtable<K,V>
extends Object
implements Cloneable, CacheImplementationInterface<K,V>, SizeMeasurable
    A hashtable which has a maximum of entries. Old entries are removed when the maximum is reached. This table is used mostly to implement a simple caching system.
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
    Rico Jansen, Michiel Meeuwissen
    See Also:
    Cache
    Move:
    consider moving to org.mmbase.cache
